headline: Diamondback Energy (FANG) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Diamondback (FANG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +8.07% and +13.36%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Diamondback: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: MIDLAND, Texas (AP) — Diamondback Energy Inc. FANG) on Monday reported third-quarter net income of $1.02 billion. On a per-share basis, the Midland, Texas-based company said it had net income of $3.51.
